      breath of fresh air    &mdash;
</h4>
            <h1 itemprop="headline">M2 iPad Air review: The everything iPad</h1>
            <h2 itemprop="description">M2 Air won't draw new buyers in, but if you like iPads, these do all you need.</h2>
            <section class="post-meta">

  
<p class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
